    "description": [
      "The remains of a campfire lie in the middle of the trail, and the undergrowth seems to have been cut back to a degree.  The small pit that holds the charred branches has weeds sprouting from its heart, testimony to the fact that this site hasn't been used in a long while.  The trellises in this area are intact and scoured clean, with no evidence of any vines."
